+# Plane Spotter
+
+A web app concept to identify aircraft you can see from your location, showing each plane’s origin and flight details.
+
+## Getting started
+
+If you are new to GitHub, start here:
+
+- [GitHub setup guide](docs/github-setup.md)
+
+## Notes for this project
+
+- Keep API keys and secrets out of GitHub by using a `.env` file (see the setup guide).
+- If you share your exact coordinates publicly, consider whether you want to obscure them for privacy.
 
EOF
